title.narrative: Intensifying targeted HIV Prevention, Care and Treatment Strategies towards achieving the three 90’s targets

description.narrative: Ethiopia - HIV - HIV/AIDS Prevention and Control Office - HAPCO. This program has the following goals: Prevent 70,000 to 80,000 new HIV infections over the investment period. Save 500,000 to 550,000 lives over the investment period. The objectives of this program are: Implement high impact and targeted prevention program. Intensify targeted HIV testing and counseling. Attain virtual elimination of MTCT. Optimize and sustain quality care and treatment. Improve access to TB, TB/HIV and DR TB treatment and care services
